postscript.p:
1. Question: Do you agree with the, opinion of
                        Secretary of State Byrnes, expressed by him over the radio last Friday,Report on the Paris Peace Conference, a radio
                            address delivered over a national network from Washington on October 18;
                            for text, see Department of State Bulletin,
                            October 27, 1946, p. 739. about increasing tension between the
                        USSR and the US?
